text: Since the Victorian era, doctors have used convalescent plasma to fight severe cases of the flu. The treatment has also shown success with two other deadly coronaviruses: MERS and SARS. But it will take studies to prove that it works to treat Covid-19. https://t.co/eIyHRhZYeB
